data.description: Seller offering $11,300 towards 2-1 buy down with acceptable offer! This can reduce your monthly payment significantly, contact agent for more details. Nestled on a half-acre lot in Godley, this home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and rustic charm. The open-concept living space boasts an abundance of natural light and high ceilings with wood beams. The heart of the home is the spacious white kitchen, featuring neutral countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large center island. Adjacent to the kitchen is a versatile room, perfect for use as a formal dining area or a home office, allowing you to tailor the space to your unique needs. Fifth bedroom is large enough to be used as a game room or however best suits you. This home, built in 2021, has been meticulously maintained, ensuring that you can move in with confidence and start creating your own cherished memories.
